    "long_instructions": "## Do This:\r\n\r\nHelp the `Painter` paint the path to the traffic cone!\r\n\r\nUse the following methods to navigate and paint each square in the path to the traffic cone:\r\n\r\n* `move()`\r\n\r\n* `turn_left()`\r\n\r\n* `take_paint()`\r\n\r\n* `paint(color)`\r\n\r\nYou can use any of these [**color names**](https://www.w3schools.com/tags/ref_colornames.asp) to paint with! For example:\r\n\r\n```\r\nkaren.paint(\"crimson\")\r\n```\r\n \r\n![](https://images.code.org/2b1e0d4fdda0c00cda888dfa4ca123d5-U1L4-L4c.gif)",
